            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Now the <strong>important</strong> part: I made a total of around <strong>25$</strong> in a single week (5 days). All things considered, it was perhaps possible to make even more, if I had left the bot running 24h‚Ää‚Äî‚Ää7 days a week.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
