            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Hold the horses‚Ä¶ because unfortunately, all good things may come to an end!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I was being careful with trying to maintain a ‚Äúnormal user behavior‚Äù, trying <strong>not</strong> to turn the bot <strong>ON</strong> for long periods of time and making just enough points to ‚Äúcash out‚Äù. I even slowed the bot down, because of it being ‚Äúto fast‚Äù and winning a game in just a few seconds. The problem was I couldn‚Äôt make it to slow, since other people were also using bots and it became a competition‚Äî to see who could make their <strong>bot faster.</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
